<p>Program in Java to list all the four digit numbers that have individual sum of 7. ie.list the numbers from 0000 to 9999 that getting the sum of each of the four digits as 7. </p>  <p>Eg: 7171 is a four digit number and the sum of each of the four digit is as 7+1+7+1 = 16 and then 1+6 = 7.So this type of numbers should be listed.</p>  <p>I wrote a code,but its not working.Code is as follows:</p>  <pre><code>public class Add  {     double i,s,n=0;     void method()     {         for(i=0000; i&lt;=9999; i++)         {             for(n=i;n&gt;0;n/=10)             {                 s=s+(n%10);              }             while(s&gt;9)             {                 for(n=s;n&gt;0;n/=10)                 {                     s=s+(n%10);                 }              }             if(s==7)             {                 System.out.println("i");             }         }      }    public static void main(String[] args)      {         Add ob=new Add();         ob.method();     }  } </code></pre>